name: O céu é loteado | The sky is alotted
description:
How much would pay for the sky?
As the ground got crowded, skyscrapes took the skies, and every inch of land was conquered by speculation, the sky is the next ground to conquer.

This is a handmade collage from magazines. Brazil based analogical art.
